id="post-4325" class="post-4325 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-art category-fun tag-game tag-play tag-toronto tag-tradecity tag-urban"><h2 class="entry-title"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2014/03/18/tradecity-a-game-that-shows-you-your-own-city/" title="Permalink to TradeCity: A Game That Shows You Your Own City" rel="bookmark">TradeCity: A Game That Shows You Your Own City</a></h2><div
class="entry-meta"> <span
class="entry-date" title="2014/03/18 9:09 am"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2014/03/18/tradecity-a-game-that-shows-you-your-own-city/" title="TradeCity: A Game That Shows You Your Own City" rel="bookmark">2014/03/18 9:09 am</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="comments-link"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2014/03/18/tradecity-a-game-that-shows-you-your-own-city/#comments">Leave a Comment</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="entry-author author vcard"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/author/administrator/" title="by Adam Clare" rel="author">Adam Clare</a></span></div><div
class="entry-content clearfix"><p><a
href="http://i2.wp.com/www.realityisagame.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/TradeCityTorontobetaPR.jpg"><img
src="http://i2.wp.com/www.realityisagame.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/TradeCityTorontobetaPR.jpg?resize=300%2C300" alt="TradeCity" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-2557" data-recalc-dims="1" /></a></p><p><a
href="http://tradecitygame.com">TradeCity: Toronto</a> is a new expeirmental art game made by <a
href="http://golbooamani.blogspot.com/">Golboo Amani</a> that begins April 1st (no fooling&#8217;) and runs to the 12th. The game is set in Toronto and you need to physically traverse the city to play the game. TradeCity will expose players to <a
href="http://tradecitygame.com/communitypartners">really cool organizations</a> in the city that they may have previously been unaware of.</p><p>I&#8217;ve had the chance to help Golboo on this project as an advisor so it&#8217;s really exciting to see the game about to start. You should sign up soon as space is limited and it looks like it&#8217;s going to be a some bizarre fun!</p><blockquote><p>TradeCity: Toronto beta is a live reality game that takes place from April 1st to 12th 2014, throughout Metro Toronto. TradeCity is an experimental art project by Toronto-based artist Golboo Amani. Amani has partnered up with various co-operative communities to design an exciting game that is both fun and challenging!</p><p>TradeCity:Toronto is an adventure based game that explores Toronto by asking Players to compete in site-specific as well as virtual challenges. There are dozens of chances to win prizes by demonstrating your gaming skills!</p><p>To play you must register in person on April 1, 2014 from 7pm to 9pm at TradeCity: Toronto beta Headquarters, University of Toronto Art Centre, 15 King&#8217;s College Circle. Players can register as a team or as individual players. You must be 18 years or older to play.</p></blockquote><p>Registration is FREE! For more information visit <a
href="http://tradecitygame.com/rulesregistration">tradecitygame.com.</a></p><p><a
href="http://www.realityisagame.com/archives/2556/play-the-test-run-of-tradecity-toronto/">Originally posted on Reality is a Game.</a></p><div
